{
  "stem": "11964.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, I wanted Teresa established in a school, because she was still very young.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to a high school, Tilden High School in Brooklyn, spoke with a wonderful lady by the name of Miss Gray.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know any English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know any English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And while I was in a displaced persons camp, I tried to learn English.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a very fine gentleman, lieutenant from Dayton, Ohio-- I forgot his name-- who took a shine to me, in terms of wanting to help me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He gave me, for example, a GI blanket so I could make myself a little cover, like a coat, for the winter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I told him I wanted to learn English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he gave me a self-teaching sort of a book that wasn't really a book, but you can learn something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember a poem that I read.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned the words of the poem. 'Who has seen the wind?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Neither you or I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the trees bow down their heads, the wind is passing by.' I remember this was the first thing that I learned in English.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were little sayings there, and he would put-- in German-- he would give me the meaning of the words, because he didn't know Polish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And little by little, I would get little English books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody gave me a German-English dictionary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I started reading and deciphering, and I started learning words.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when we came to the United States, first thing I wanted to do is to establish the fact that Teresa's going to get education.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this Miss Gray took her under her wings, and she says, she will do the best she can.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She will give her a tutorial.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
